%% ============================================================================
%% NU-AURA HRMS - Authentication & Authorization Flow
%% JWT + MFA + RBAC
%%
%% Render at: https://mermaid.live
%% ============================================================================

sequenceDiagram
    participant User as 👤 User
    participant Browser as 🌐 Browser
    participant NextJS as Next.js Frontend
    participant API as Spring Boot API
    participant Security as Security Service
    participant Redis as Redis Cache
    participant DB as PostgreSQL
    participant MFA as MFA Service<br/>(TOTP/SMS)
    participant Email as Email Service

    %% === STEP 1: Initial Login ===
    Note over User,Email: 🔐 STEP 1: Initial Login (Username/Password)

    User->>Browser: Enter email & password
    Browser->>NextJS: Submit login form
    NextJS->>API: POST /api/auth/login<br/>{"email", "password"}

    API->>DB: SELECT * FROM users<br/>WHERE email = ? AND status = 'ACTIVE'
    DB-->>API: User record + tenant_id + roles

    alt Invalid credentials
        API-->>Browser: 401 Unauthorized
        Browser-->>User: "Invalid credentials"
    end

    API->>API: BCrypt.matches(password, user.passwordHash)

    alt Password incorrect
        API-->>Browser: 401 Unauthorized
        Browser-->>User: "Invalid credentials"
    end

    API->>DB: SELECT mfa_enabled FROM users<br/>WHERE id = ?
    DB-->>API: mfa_enabled = true

    alt MFA Enabled
        API->>MFA: Generate TOTP token
        MFA-->>API: TOTP challenge
        API->>Redis: SET mfa:pending:{sessionId}<br/>{"userId", "tenantId", "expiresIn": 300}
        API-->>Browser: 200 OK + tempToken<br/>{"mfaRequired": true}
        Browser-->>User: Display MFA input screen

        Note over User,Email: 🔐 STEP 2: MFA Verification

        User->>Browser: Enter MFA code (6 digits)
        Browser->>NextJS: Submit MFA code
        NextJS->>API: POST /api/auth/mfa/verify<br/>{"tempToken", "code"}

        API->>Redis: GET mfa:pending:{sessionId}
        Redis-->>API: Pending MFA data

        API->>MFA: Verify TOTP code
        MFA-->>API: Code valid ✅

        alt MFA code invalid
            API-->>Browser: 401 Unauthorized
            Browser-->>User: "Invalid MFA code"
        end

        API->>Redis: DEL mfa:pending:{sessionId}
    end

    Note over User,Email: 🔐 STEP 3: Load User Permissions

    API->>Security: loadUserPermissions(userId, tenantId)
    Security->>DB: SELECT rp.permission, rp.scope<br/>FROM role_permissions rp<br/>JOIN user_roles ur ON ur.role_id = rp.role_id<br/>WHERE ur.user_id = ? AND ur.tenant_id = ?
    DB-->>Security: 300+ permissions with scopes

    Security->>Security: Build permission map<br/>{"employee.create": "ALL",<br/> "leave.approve": "TEAM"}

    Security->>Security: Get accessible apps
    Security->>DB: SELECT app_code FROM user_app_access<br/>WHERE user_id = ?
    DB-->>Security: ["HRMS", "LMS", "PSA"]

    Note over User,Email: 🔐 STEP 4: Generate JWT Token

    API->>Security: Generate lightweight JWT

    Security->>Security: Create JWT payload:<br/>{<br/> "sub": "user@example.com",<br/> "userId": "uuid",<br/> "tenantId": "uuid",<br/> "appCode": "HRMS",<br/> "roles": ["HR_ADMIN"],<br/> "employeeId": "uuid",<br/> "sessionId": "uuid"<br/>}<br/>Size: 560 bytes

    Security->>Redis: SET user:permissions:{sessionId}<br/>{"permissions": {...},<br/> "accessibleApps": [...],<br/> "cachedAt": "timestamp"}<br/>TTL: 5 minutes

    Security->>Security: Sign JWT with HS512

    Security-->>API: JWT token (560 bytes)

    API->>API: Create httpOnly cookie<br/>Set-Cookie: token={jwt};<br/>HttpOnly; Secure; SameSite=Strict

    API-->>Browser: 200 OK<br/>{"token": "...",<br/> "expiresIn": 3600,<br/> "user": {"name", "email", "role"}}

    Browser->>Browser: Store JWT in httpOnly cookie
    Browser->>Browser: Store user info in Zustand

    Browser-->>User: Redirect to dashboard

    Note over User,Email: 🔐 STEP 5: Subsequent API Requests with Permission Check

    User->>Browser: Click "Create Employee"
    Browser->>NextJS: Navigate to /employees/new
    NextJS->>API: POST /api/employees<br/>Authorization: Bearer {JWT}

    API->>API: Extract JWT from header
    API->>API: Validate JWT signature
    API->>API: Check JWT expiry

    alt JWT expired
        API-->>Browser: 401 Unauthorized
        Browser->>Browser: Clear auth state
        Browser-->>User: Redirect to login
    end

    API->>Security: Check permission<br/>("employee.create", "ALL")

    Security->>Redis: GET user:permissions:{sessionId}

    alt Cache hit
        Redis-->>Security: Cached permissions ✅
        Note right of Security: Fast path: 2ms
    else Cache miss
        Redis-->>Security: null
        Security->>DB: Reload permissions (slow query)
        DB-->>Security: Permission list
        Security->>Redis: SET user:permissions:{sessionId}<br/>TTL: 5 min
        Note right of Security: Slow path: 45ms
    end

    Security->>Security: Check if user has<br/>"employee.create" with scope "ALL"

    alt Permission denied
        Security-->>API: PermissionDeniedException
        API-->>Browser: 403 Forbidden
        Browser-->>User: "You don't have permission"
    end

    Security-->>API: Permission granted ✅

    API->>API: Execute business logic<br/>Create employee record

    API->>DB: INSERT INTO employees<br/>(tenant_id, name, email, ...)<br/>VALUES (?, ?, ...)

    DB-->>API: Employee created

    API-->>Browser: 201 Created<br/>{"id": "uuid", "name": "..."}

    Browser-->>User: "Employee created successfully"

    Note over User,Email: 🔐 STEP 6: Logout

    User->>Browser: Click "Logout"
    Browser->>NextJS: Logout action
    NextJS->>API: POST /api/auth/logout

    API->>Redis: DEL user:permissions:{sessionId}
    API->>Redis: DEL user:session:{sessionId}

    API->>API: Clear httpOnly cookie

    API-->>Browser: 200 OK

    Browser->>Browser: Clear Zustand auth state
    Browser->>Browser: Clear JWT cookie

    Browser-->>User: Redirect to login page
